OL,3,CFired store manager to meet with
OL,4,CMorrisons boss after tackling
OL,5,Cshoplifter
OL,7,FThe Chief Executive of Morrisons will
OL,8,Fmeet this week with dismissed store
OL,9,Fmanager Sean Egan, after he was fired
OL,10,Ffor tackling a shoplifter.
OL,12,FSean Egan, 46, was a manager at the
OL,13,FAldridge store near Walsall for 29
OL,14,Fyears, when he was dismissed following
OL,15,Fthe incident in December.
OL,17,FA repeat shoplifter became abusive and
OL,18,Fspat in Mr Egan's face during a
OL,19,Fconfrontation over stolen goods. Mr
OL,20,FEgan then escorted the shoplifter from
OL,21,Fthe store.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777309554
OL,3,CFired store manager to meet with
OL,4,CMorrisons boss after tackling
OL,5,Cshoplifter
OL,7,FMorrisons dismissed Mr Egan on the
OL,8,Fgrounds of not following its "deter-
OL,9,Fand-not-detain" policy.
OL,11,FMr Egan said he has received a
OL,12,F"variety" of job offers from other
OL,13,Fsupermarkets, but will not rule out
OL,14,Fgoing back to Morrisons.
OL,16,F"Understand the the public interest"
OL,18,FAfter a letter from his local MP Wendy
OL,19,FMorton MP, the Chief Executive of
OL,20,FMorrisons, Rami Baitieh, has agreed to
OL,21,Fmeet with Mr Egan.
OL,26,@|D@Vrr
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777309554
OL,3,CFired store manager to meet with
OL,4,CMorrisons boss after tackling
OL,5,Cshoplifter
OL,7,FBaitieh said: "I am meeting Sean next
OL,8,Fweek and understand the the public
OL,9,Finterest this case has generated.
OL,11,F"The provocation Sean experienced has
OL,12,Fbeen an unacceptable reality of
OL,13,Fworking on the shopfloor and we are
OL,14,Fcontinuing the take wide-ranging
OL,15,Factions to address the threat of
OL,16,Fshoplifting and abuse in our stores."
OL,18,FHe added: "We have so far refrained
OL,19,Ffrom detailed public comment because
OL,20,Fwe do not believe that this would be
OL,21,Fhelpful for Sean.
OL,26,@oD@Frr
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777309554
OL,3,CFired store manager to meet with
OL,4,CMorrisons boss after tackling
OL,5,Cshoplifter
OL,7,F"To be clear, the public reporting of
OL,8,Fthe incident does not reflect the full
OL,9,Ffact of the situation or fully
OL,10,Fconsider the unintended consequences
OL,11,Fthat can occur when colleagues
OL,12,Fphysically confront criminals."
OL,14,FMore than a hundred people gathered
OL,15,Foutside Morrisons on Saturday 25
OL,16,FApril, holding placards that read
OL,17,F'Hero Sean' and 'Sean the hero,
OL,18,FMorrisons the zero'.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777309554
OL,3,CFired store manager to meet with
OL,4,CMorrisons boss after tackling
OL,5,Cshoplifter
OL,7,FMr Egan said the support from
OL,8,Fprotestors has been "uplifting", but
OL,9,Fsays he does not want to damage
OL,10,FMorrisons' reputation.
OL,12,FThe shoplifter has since been
OL,13,Fconvicted and sentenced in relation to
OL,14,Fthe incident.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
